5:
You shall find no mercy here, pawns
of the heavens...
8:
Here, we shall break the chains of
fate that bind our kin—and those
which bind the very stars!
17:
There... That should be the last
airborne foe—
28:
That was simply stunning! I admit it
overshadowed our own display
down here a bit, but still!
31: Clearly this is a sign of our victory—
91:
We must pull the line back, into the
Kaleidoscope. While we concentrate
our strength there, we can try to find
an escape route to another world.
96:
B-but you were the one who said we
must make our stand here, no?! We
would lose our chance to
counterattack!
100:
The enemy's strength has far
surpassed our every expectation.
Staying here would only mean
certain death for all.
109:
We run away this time, but then
what? We can't escape them
forever...
113:
We keep fighting. We retreat when
necessary, but only to ensure we
survive to fight again. Then, we do it
over again—until our strength is
spent!
126:
This dark energy is... coming from
below!
130:
The darkness is spreading
somehow... Is it the Kaleidoscope
itself?
137:
No, it couldn't be...
But this...
141: It's the power of the curse...
167:
All right, ya lassies. Me old bones
could use a bit of yer help!
172:
The Flame of Courage burns within
all of you!
177:
Lend me your ears—please hear my
song!
